snippet.title: Gamescom Exhibition — "Tales of the Luofu: A New Chapter" | Honkai: Star Rail
snippet.description:
"Speaking of the Merlin's Claw, these shining streets are ceaselessly drowned by her awesome tales and magnificent deeds. This guest here asked: Won't it get boring just hearing about her glory alone? Heh? Well, dear guest, I think you underestimate the speed at which our general performs these feats of legends, so take heed and listen up!"
